replies.body:
Nami main here

I almost always run Sorcery as Aery, Manaflow band, Transcendence, and Scorch, then for my secondary page I run Chrysalis and Revitalize on the Resolve tree.
Build I run: {{item:3504}} {{item:3174}} {{item:3107}} {{item:2065}} {{item:3117}} {{item:3190}} 
Situational: {{item:3222}} {{item:3116}} {{item:3905}} 

If it seems like a really difficult all-in type of matchup I'll take Resolve as my primary with Guardian, Bone Plating, Chrysalis, and Revitalize. Then my secondary page as Inspiration with Perfect timing and Future's Market (or Cosmic insight.. preference).
